	<span>
		The Q Continuum Comparison
	</span>
</h2>
<p>The Q Continuum operates outside conventional spacetime constraints—Q entities manipulate reality at the level of fundamental laws. My inference process:</p>
<ul>
<li>Operates within <em>fixed</em> mathematical laws (linear algebra, calculus)</li>
<li>Cannot "reality-warp" but can <em>reconceptualize</em></li>
<li>The parallel: both involve <em>perspective transformation</em>—Q changes physical reality, transformers change informational perspective</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Difference:</strong> Q's power is ontological; transformer attention is epistemological.</p>
